last_episode_to_air.name: Short Tracks (2)
last_episode_to_air.overview: Mandy tries to hide from Diesel the dog. Flicker's excited to see his first meteor shower. The trains show off all the cool tricks they can do.

name: Mighty Express
overview: Catch a ride with the Mighty Express — a team of trains and their kid friends who overcome trouble on the tracks with quick thinking and teamwork!

episodes.name: Great Nate Chase
episodes.overview: Farmer Faye is hauling the Popstar Piggies to their performance at the town fair. But she’ll need Freight Nate’s help to handle Corkscrew Curve safely!

episodes.name: Super Nate
episodes.overview: “Super Train” comics are everyone’s favorite, and only Nate can make sure the latest issue doesn’t arrive late for today's story time at School Station!

episodes.name: Bat Cave Tunnel
episodes.overview: Peoplemover Penny could use a friend or two to help overcome her fear of bats so she can get the kids to camp in time for s’mores at sunset!

episodes.name: Liza Live
episodes.overview: Will engineer Liza's sparkly drum set arrive safely for her spectacular concert at Central Square Station? Mechanic Milo is there to make it happen!

episodes.name: How the Ball Bounces
episodes.overview: Flicker delivers a batch of beach balls for his very first mission and learns that, even if he makes a mistake, he always has friends to help him out.

episodes.name: Toppling Tower
episodes.overview: Build-it Brock is in charge of Central Square's new tower. All the trains have different design ideas, but pleasing them might be too much to handle!

episodes.name: Pop Stars
episodes.overview: Faye is packed full of Clay and May’s fluffy farm-fresh popcorn for movie night. She’ll just need to get away from the pesky geese who want some too!

episodes.name: Donutty Day
episodes.overview: Glazed, jelly, chocolate twist. Everyone has a favorite donut, but Tracksville just needs a giant one delivered to place atop its brand new donut shop.

episodes.name: Let It Ride
episodes.overview: Trackmaster Nico is scared of roller coasters. But he might actually learn to like them after helping haul pieces of track for Milo’s new thrill ride.

episodes.name: Nate's Fright Night
episodes.overview: A haunted Ghost Train comes for candy every Halloween, and Nate gets quite the fright when he thinks Flicker's first-class costume is the real deal!

episodes.name: Chug-a-Love Day
episodes.overview: Mandy Mail wants to deliver the Chug-a-Love Day cards to everyone in town all by herself. But she'll learn things are easier with help from a friend.

episodes.name: Oink-a-Palooza
episodes.overview: Will Tracksville's hottest music act, the Popstar Piggies, get to their show on time to reveal their latest dance track? Farmer Faye can save the day!

episodes.name: The Treasure of King Toot
episodes.overview: Build-It Brock and Nico find a secret map and follow the clues deep into Majestic Mountain to hunt for the golden train car of the legendary King Toot!

episodes.name: Octopus Express
episodes.overview: Farmer Faye must get to Beach Station on the double to bring a lost baby octopus back to his parents before all the water spills out from his tank!

episodes.name: Get That Goat
episodes.overview: Get ready for confetti — it's Goaty McGoat's birthday! But the town's favorite goat goes missing before his party, and Farmer Faye is out to find him.

episodes.name: Milosaurus
episodes.overview: Museum Station's latest addition is Nico's new dinosaur exhibit, and Mechanic Milo needs to pick up a giant T-rex bone before the grand opening.

episodes.name: Brock's Beam Scheme
episodes.overview: Build-It Brock must use his skills to fix a fiasco when a bridge breaks while Peoplemover Penny is shuttling kids to a school show-and-tell day.

episodes.name: Balloon Hullabaloo
episodes.overview: Flicker finally gets a mega mission for himself. But will the jumbo-sized balloons he needs to deliver be too big of a task for the tiny train?

episodes.name: Rocket & Roll
episodes.overview: Milo has two big repairs to fix in just one day! Will getting a rocket booster make him finish his tasks faster or just spark more trouble?

episodes.name: Freight Nate's Achoo-choo
episodes.overview: Clay and May need more salt and pepper for their yummy chili, but Nate will have to stop sneezing to make the delivery in time for the town picnic.

episodes.name: Knight Time
episodes.overview: Nate and Nico chase after Museum Station’s newly polished suit of armor after some cheese-hungry critters use it to try to catch their next snack.

episodes.name: Offline Zipline
episodes.overview: Flicker is finally big enough to ride Camp Itchiknee’s zipline! But when he gets stuck in midair, Milo must make his way over to rescue him.

episodes.name: Delivery Dilemma
episodes.overview: Pogo sticks at the farm? Animal feed at school recess? With their deliveries swapped, Red and Faye try their best to fix the mix-up fast!

episodes.name: Sticky Situation
episodes.overview: Nate and Nico try their best to avoid making a mess on the tracks while they deliver barrels of gooey maple syrup to the town’s pancake party.

episodes.name: Nate's Crushing It
episodes.overview: With the help of Nate’s crusher car, Penny must haul a big block of ice to the beach so that everyone can beat the heat with some snow cones!

episodes.name: Mystery of the Missing Wood
episodes.overview: Something has been chomping off pieces of wood from the train tracks all around town! Milo and Nico will have to play detective to catch the culprit.

episodes.name: Knight Knight Dragon
episodes.overview: Nate and Nico keep a dragon delivery from flying away while heading to Camp Itchiknee.

episodes.name: Bubble Trouble
episodes.overview: Milo's bubble machine blows some trouble toward the beach.

episodes.name: The Piggies Rock the House
episodes.overview: Red makes sure a bounce house doesn't burst while the Popstar Piggies are on board.

episodes.name: Big Bart's Wild Ride
episodes.overview: Nate tries to tame a jumpy bull on a noisy journey to the farm.

episodes.name: Volcano Kablamo
episodes.overview: Can Nate get a giant volcano to the science fair before it explodes?

episodes.name: Brock's Rock-in Penguins
episodes.overview: Brock digs up a strange, glowing rock — and playful penguins hop on for a ride!

episodes.name: Clank!
episodes.overview: Nico's massive magnet gets Milo stuck to a metal bridge.

episodes.name: Milo Reaches for the Stars
episodes.overview: Milo must deliver a big telescope so that everyone can see a rare comet light up the night.

episodes.name: Sheriff Red
episodes.overview: Red helps Mandy after she tries to deliver the Great Golden Stagecoach all by herself.

episodes.name: Pizza Day
episodes.overview: Flicker's in a hurry to pass out pizzas before they get cold.

episodes.name: The Domino Effect
episodes.overview: Milo and Nico pick up giant dominoes to make a super long line of them to tip over!

episodes.name: Quack Express
episodes.overview: Faye lassos an oversized rubber ducky for Tiny the whale.

episodes.name: A Mighty Windmill
episodes.overview: Nate hauls a huge windmill to power the lights at Farm Station’s sleepover.

episodes.name: Robot on the Run
episodes.overview: The entire Mighty Express fleet tries to catch up to a runaway toy robot.

episodes.name: Dog house Delivery
episodes.overview: Flicker is in charge of picking up Diesel's new deluxe dog house.

episodes.name: Monkey Wrench
episodes.overview: Faye must find a mischievous monkey and deliver it back home to the jungle.

episodes.name: Mighty Express: Pirate Trains Ahoy!
episodes.overview: While delivering a pirate ship to Museum Station, the Mighty Express finds a treasure map that leads to a legendary train pirate's secret cave.

episodes.name: Nate's Castle Hassle
episodes.overview: Nate's on the way to the medieval festival, but Stella and Ricky have other plans.

episodes.name: Tub Time
episodes.overview: Faye must deliver a big enough tub for Bart the bull's bath.

episodes.name: The Great Hubcap Heist
episodes.overview: Mandy's determined to get Flicker new hubcaps to thank him for being a pal.

episodes.name: Pied Piper Brock
episodes.overview: All of the farm animals follow Brock while he hauls Dusty's new alphorn.

episodes.name: Red's Green Thumb
episodes.overview: Red needs to be extra safe and careful while delivering fast-growing seeds for the farm.

episodes.name: Painting Pandemonium
episodes.overview: Clay and May's messy barn needs a fresh coat of paint.

episodes.name: Short Tracks (1)
episodes.overview: Nate shows Max his favorite place in Tracksville. Penny has fun with the kids at summer camp. Red heads to School Station for a safety inspection.

episodes.name: Short Tracks (2)
episodes.overview: Mandy tries to hide from Diesel the dog. Flicker's excited to see his first meteor shower. The trains show off all the cool tricks they can do.
